{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kombi is a fun, minimalist, grid-based puzzle game. The aim of the game is to move tiles across the board, picking up points along the way, in order to end up with a single tile with a value that matches the number of the target tile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/extras/sc1.png?t=1739310182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While it starts off simple, the later campaign levels introduce enough complexity to keep you entertained and scratching your head for hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/extras/sc2.png?t=1739310182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And once you've completed the campaign levels, you are free to enjoy an unlimited selection of custom levels, allowing you to play the game indefinitely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/extras/sc3.png?t=1739310182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are no limitations or locked levels, each level can be completed in any number of turns, though there is a special completion badge awarded if a level is completed within a certain number of turns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/extras/sc4.png?t=1739310182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100 campaign levels of various grid sizes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A custom level generator allowing you to choose any difficulty you want</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minimalist design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Relaxing background music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlimited UNDO options if you make a mistake</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 different themes, including dark mode</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3492330?t=1739310182","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3492330?t=1739310182","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/e964284b90b96527f78f10632c86e69b7a3b0412/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739310182","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/e964284b90b96527f78f10632c86e69b7a3b0412/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739310182","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kombi is a fun, minimalist, grid-based puzzle game. The aim of the game is to move tiles across the board, picking up points along the way, in order to end up with a single tile with a value that matches the number of the target tile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/extras/sc1.png?t=1739310182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While it starts off simple, the later campaign levels introduce enough complexity to keep you entertained and scratching your head for hours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/extras/sc2.png?t=1739310182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And once you've completed the campaign levels, you are free to enjoy an unlimited selection of custom levels, allowing you to play the game indefinitely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/extras/sc3.png?t=1739310182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are no limitations or locked levels, each level can be completed in any number of turns, though there is a special completion badge awarded if a level is completed within a certain number of turns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/extras/sc4.png?t=1739310182\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100 campaign levels of various grid sizes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A custom level generator allowing you to choose any difficulty you want</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Minimalist design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Relaxing background music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlimited UNDO options if you make a mistake</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 different themes, including dark mode</p></li></ul>","developers":["Kouzii"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492330/header.jpg?t=1739310182","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257095853,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257095853/movie480.mp4?t=1739310180","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257095853/movie_max.mp4?t=1739310180"},"name":"Kombi Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai